org.peertrust.tnviz.app
Class TNNode

java.lang.Object
  javax.swing.tree.DefaultMutableTreeNode
      org.jgraph.graph.DefaultGraphCell
          org.peertrust.tnviz.app.TNNode
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, javax.swing.tree.MutableTreeNode, javax.swing.tree.TreeNode, org.jgraph.graph.GraphCell
public final class TNNode
extends org.jgraph.graph.DefaultGraphCell

The TNNode class is a custom version of the DefaultGraphCell class. It contains needed information like ports, address and alias data. This data can be easily accessed through the class methods.
